to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Contact Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[10422,1420],"id":"58e72920-7173-4d1f-9ccb-6b225c6e97eb","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hourly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 1 h. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Pull Side A (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"89fc7b50-c06f-ca54-6ab2-5ce186155df2","name":"Note: Hourly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side A (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,250],"id":"15215a9a-12c5-4159-99cd-57be97d6783c","name":"Note: Pull Side A (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Pull Side B (Notion)\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff the Two Systems · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,790],"id":"2a26be41-7944-3d41-58ae-f3cd1e8e7b85","name":"Note: Pull Side B (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff the Two Systems\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Missing in Notion · ②→ Count In-Sync Rows · ③→ Apply Updates to Notion · ④→ Backfill into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"ea5d5b18-37b9-7344-e809-10d0c5cf76b7","name":"Note: Diff the Two Systems"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Missing in Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,-80],"id":"dbd7bd42-e1a1-49e3-d1b7-1d46d05b4dfa","name":"Note: Create Missing in Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count In-Sync Rows\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Gather Sync Results","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,340],"id":"35c9adbb-3685-e516-333a-d060679e0727","name":"Note: Count In-Sync Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Updates to Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,760],"id":"0bbdb4b0-2a9c-dbf6-15d9-21996d0211bb","name":"Note: Apply Updates to Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Backfill into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,1180],"id":"e4e44e50-63c4-00dc-28c1-afacca9d3e